stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> OpenJoinPage
    OpenJoinPage --> EnterPIN : Type invite code
    EnterPIN --> SubmitPIN
    SubmitPIN --> ValidatePIN : POST /api/environments/join/
    ValidatePIN --> InvalidPIN : Code not found
    InvalidPIN --> EnterPIN
    ValidatePIN --> CheckExistingMembership
    CheckExistingMembership --> AlreadyMember : Membership exists
    AlreadyMember --> ShowDashboard
    CheckExistingMembership --> CreateMembership : New member
    CreateMembership --> AssignRole : security_analyst role
    AssignRole --> ShowDashboard
    ShowDashboard --> [*]